NFTModule.name: NFTModule
NFTModule.remarks: This module provides ERC721 functionality. It is used to mint 1 of 1 NFTs.

methods.name: getAll
methods.summary: Fetches all NFTs that are contained by the module.

examples.node:
const module = sdk.getNFTModule("{{module_address}}");
const nfts = await module.getAll();
